  <description><![CDATA[<p>Nestled next to the shores of Lake Maggiore, Hotel Splendid offers a touch of grandeur in beautiful surroundings. The laidback resort of Baveno is just a ten-minute walk away and you can reach the popular town of Stresa in just five minutes by taxi.</p>
<p>This grand and stylish hotel has been decorated in an elegant style with dark wood furnishings, parquet floors and superb outside areas including a large decked terrace with comfortable sofas, an outdoor pool and a private beach with direct access into the waters of the lake. A large wellness area is well equipped with a sauna, Turkish bath, Jacuzzi and salt grotto. The hotel’s a la carte restaurant, Pallanza enjoys stunning lake views and serves delicious local and international cuisine. After dinner, the bar provides a welcome retreat with homely furnishings and direct access to the large terrace.</p>
<p>Transfer time: approx. 1 hour by coach.</p>]]></description>
