  <facilityDescription><![CDATA[<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Restaurants &amp; Bars</strong></span></p>
<p><strong>Pallanza Restaurant</strong> is open for breakfast, lunch and dinner and serves regional and international cuisine in a lovely setting overlooking the lake.</p>
<p><strong>Bar &amp; Piazzetta</strong> is an elegant space where you can enjoy a drink inside or on the terrace that’s furnished with garden sofas and umbrellas.</p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Pool &amp; Beach</strong></span></p>
<p>Choose to relax by the lovely outdoor pool or by the hotel’s private beach that has a platform leading into the lake. Both are equipped with loungers and umbrella. The pool and beach are normally in use from mid May to mid September. Pool towels are provided.</p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Wellness</strong></span></p>
<p>Hotel Splendid has a lovely wellness area with a Jacuzzi, salt grotto, sauna, Turkish bath and a fitness room.</p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>General Facilities</strong></span></p>
<ul>
<li>Free wifi</li>
</ul>]]></facilityDescription>
